In the documentation page https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA064/Connecting+to+an+LDAP+Directory it is stated
{quote}
Ensure that this is an administrator user for the LDAP engine. For example, in Active Directory the user will need to be a member of the built-in Administrators group{quote}

